 inclusive settings, and to promote literacy and the use of technology in social studies classrooms"--cProvided by publisher.  a41 0aSocial sciencesxStudy and teaching (Secondary)zUnited States.  aH 62.5 U5 S56 2014c1hUAED-Bi0162035210168  aH 62.5 U5 S56 2014wLCc1i0162035210168lFLOOR_2mUAEDUCp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu1/9/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n97020534bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/33736652